672
00:51:54,380 --> 00:51:56,920
[SPEAKER_01] dakle tu ne može biti nikakve ravnopravnosti.

673
00:51:56,920 --> 00:51:58,699
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, tu Hrvatska se mora puno oštrije

674
00:51:58,699 --> 00:51:59,739
